Package com.example.parser

Class configurationBaseListener

java.lang.Object
com.example.parser.configurationBaseListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
configurationListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
public class configurationBaseListener extends Object implements configurationListener
This class provides an empty implementation of configurationListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
